race.comment: WE ARE ONE (7) boasts strong form at this track having won two times from four starts. Below best last time at Geelong (26.32) in a Grade 5 NP, finishing a 4 length seventh. Makes strong appeal on best. GOLD VENOM (1) stuck on well last time to finish 1.2 lengths back in third (24.50) at this track in a Grade 5 over 425m. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Overdue and is among the main hopes. REBEL THINKER (2) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Lizard Country (28.78) in a T3 RSTW. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Expected to be in the finish again. LIONESS EYES (6) can feature with the right run.
